Toronto-TMC: Completing work for COT Project - 25ECS-RD-102LR. Sidewalks will be closed one at a time, always allowing pedestrians to have access down the road. Paving closures will allow local traffic at all times. Recon & Paving closures will be set up once per activity and drivable lane will be provided outside of work areas during recon.
